snippet.title: Woman Accused Of Stealing Pastor’s Truck 2 Years Ago Back In Jail Accused Of Same Crime
snippet.description:
A Tulsa woman who got a deferred sentence just a few years ago for stealing a pastor's truck, is back in jail, accused of stealing another vehicle. ***
